ing on if it was tips or tolls day. Then I just did the same for columns but I would focus on the corner route to start that covered the half of the grid with the most vertical routes.\"},\"trial_type\":\"survey-text\",\"trial_index\":415,\"time_elapsed\":1818763,\"internal_node_id\":\"0.0-372.0\",\"final_zoom_factor\":0.6,\"blue_key\":\"P\",\"green_key\":\"Q\",\"correctCount\":12,\"total_n_questions\":12,\"quiz_passed\":true,\"bonus_accuracy\":0.9},{\"rt\":55751,\"response\":{\"tips_vs_tolls\":\"I used the same initial strategy because I felt like it gave me a good forecast of what rows / columns to hit or avoid. Then after the first choice my choices changed depending on toll or tip day to ensure I made the most / paid the least\"},\"trial_type\":\"survey-text\",\"trial_index\":416,\"time_elapsed\":1874517,\"internal_node_id\":\"0.0-373.0\",\"final_zoom_factor\":0.6,\"blue_key\":\"P\",\"green_key\":\"Q\",\"correctCount\":12,\"total_n_questions\":12,\"quiz_passed\":true,\"bonus_accuracy\":0.9},{\"rt\":44695,\"response\":{\"rows_vs_columns\":\"Yes, already explained in previous answers that I used the first choice to cut across the grid so to speak in order to ascertain which rows or columns were best\"},\"trial_type\":\"survey-text\",\"trial_index\":417,\"time_elapsed\":1919213,\"internal_node_id\":\"0.0-374.0\",\"final_zoom_factor\":0.6,\"blue_key\":\"P\",\"green_key\":\"Q\",\"correctCount\":12,\"total_n_questions\":12,\"quiz_passed\":true,\"bonus_accuracy\":0.9},{\"rt\":37293,\"response\":{\"lookahead\":\"I would scan them at the start quickly, to see where most of the horizontal (for rows) or vertical (column day) routes were\"},\"trial_type\":\"survey-text\",\"trial_index\":418,\"time_elapsed\":1956509,\"internal_node_id\":\"0.0-375.0\",\"final_zoom_factor\":0.6,\"blue_key\":\"P\",\"green_key\":\"Q\",\"correctCount\":12,\"total_n_questions\":12,\"quiz_passed\":true,\"bonus_accuracy\":0.9},{\"rt\":15650,\"response\":{\"other_comments\":\"It was really a genuinel